CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 14, 1954, page 26, reads: "Archie's Auto Wash - If it's a quick, thorough car wash you want, drive out to Archie's Auto Wash at 8050 Bennett Street and let his capable crew sat your car to glistening. The workers are shown doing a fine job on one of Archie's many satisfied customers. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Archie's Car Wash with men wiping down Pontiac emerging from Washmobile, with sign reading "Now Open" on left, 8050 Bennett Street, Homewood
